    • Class com.ibm.avatar.api.exceptions.CircularDependencyException extends TextAnalyticsException implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      -6177143937430252981L

      • Serialized Fields

        • modulesInTheCycleVsErrorMarker

          Map<K,V> modulesInTheCycleVsErrorMarker
          Map of circularly dependent source modules. The key of the map is source module name, which is part of the cycle and the value is the list of location of the import statements, importing the next module in the cycle. Location is a Pair of String and Integer, where string contains the absolute path to the aql file containing the import statement and the integer points to the line number of the import statement.
